Adding the steps to reproduce:
1. Use the app below in app.js file 
{code}
var win = Ti.UI.createWindow({
	backgroundColor:'black'
});

var view = Ti.UI.createView({
	backgroundColor:'white',
	width:40,
	height:40
});

win.add(view);
win.open();
{code}
2. Add the line below in tiapp.xml file of project
  <property name="ti.ui.defaultunit">abc</property>
3. Run the app

Expected result:
Display warning during packaging, use default system value

Actual result
No warning is displayed.
